{"tid":247772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國28歲已婚女教師邀請到家作客-與丈夫灌醉男學生性侵囚兩年","createTime":"2017-05-18T05:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T06:29:18.000Z","uid":30924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48989b9a6228bb705368358fe237f99e0454d36d","tid":247772,"uid":30924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:23:20.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】美國俄亥俄州28歲已婚女教師Jessica Storer，去年11月與丈夫Derrick灌醉一名18歲男學生，Jessica最後更「執屍」性侵，造成男學生心理創傷，並多次試圖自殺。昨日Jessica遭判刑兩年，終身列入性侵犯名單中，而丈夫也將面臨六個月徒刑。<br />\n<br />\nJessica是潘朵拉吉爾勃高中（Pandora-Gilboa High School）的代課老師，同時也擔任<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地方媽媽</span></span>，去年11月，她與丈夫Derrick邀請18歲男學生，以及其他同學到家中作客，Derrick卻對男學生灌酒，導致他不勝酒力，在夫妻家中過夜。隔天早晨，Jessica竟對酒醉未醒的男學生「執屍」性侵。<br />\n<br />\n根據庭訊紀錄，該名男學生曾透過信件表示，他很信任Jessica，沒想到卻遭性侵，心裡的陰影讓他多次試圖自殺，目前仍努力克服。Jessica則在庭上承認自己很自責，很抱歉造成他莫大的傷害，最後這名女老師被判刑兩年，終身登記為性侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/SXdDC3ZciuURvSHmPK9Sig--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAw/http://l.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/GLB/2017-05-17/522cc400-3ad5-11e7-8927-d3592ea710da_teacherrape.jpeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSXdDC3ZciuURvSHmPK9Sig--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fl.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2017-05-17%2F522cc400-3ad5-11e7-8927-d3592ea710da_teacherrape.jpeg&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=b1130957\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/SXdDC3ZciuURvSHmPK9Sig--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAw/http://l.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/GLB/2017-05-17/522cc400-3ad5-11e7-8927-d3592ea710da_teacherrape.jpeg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來真係有地方媽媽需要愛"},{"pid":"7ea5c12948dc84573bc2f5392829f97b8b6e8735","tid":247772,"uid":30924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com